1. *Najvažnije* je da se trudimo da budemo srećni. (The most important thing is that we try to be happy.)
2. On je shvatio *najvažnije* lekcije. (He understood the most important lessons.)
3. *Najvažnije* je da budemo zahvalni. (The most important thing is that we are grateful.)
4. *Najvažnije* je da budemo ljubazni. (The most important thing is that we are kind.)
5. On je shvatio *najvažnije* principove. (He understood the most important principles.)